xyz.swatt.data_mapping_validator

Class SqlPojoCollectionMappingValidator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.swatt.data_mapping_validator.AbstractDataMapping<T>
      • xyz.swatt.data_mapping_validator.SqlPojoCollectionMappingValidator<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataMappingValidator<T> 

    @LogMethods
public class SqlPojoCollectionMappingValidator<T>
extends AbstractDataMapping<T>
    Use this class to validate that 2 different Collections of SqlPojos are equal, compairing their Column Values.

    Note: The Column Value Types are defined by T.

    Note: This class is used instead of direct comparison, to simplify large batches of comparisons, and to provide common functionality.

    Author:
    Brandon Dudek (BrandonDudek)

    • Method Detail

      • consolidateOnDestination

        public static java.util.Collection<SqlPojoCollectionMappingValidator> consolidateOnDestination(java.util.Collection<SqlPojoCollectionMappingValidator> _mappings)
        Will combine Mappings that have the same Destination Row(s) and Column.

        Or, for the mappings that do not have a Destination Row/Column, they will be combined on Destination Value(s).

        Note: Mapping Names will also be combined.

        Parameters:
        _mappings - The Mappings to consolidate.
        Returns:
        All Mappings, after combining.
